verbose_text: In this study, our results demonstrated that OGD or H 2 O 2 increased cell death, including apoptosis, decreased Deltapsi m and increased the subsequent cytosolic translocation of Cyt.C, thereby promoting downstream caspase activation, resulting in increased levels of caspase-9, caspase-3, PARP (the substrate of caspase-3), anti-apoptotic protein Bcl-2 and pro apoptotic protein Bax in the cytoplasm.
